INDICATOR_NAME: Unemployment, youth total (% of total labor force ages 15-24) (modeled ILO estimate)
SOURCE_NOTE: Youth unemployment refers to the share of the labor force ages 15-24 without work but available for and seeking employment.
SOURCE_ORGANIZATION: International Labour Organization. “ILO Modelled Estimates and Projections database (ILOEST)” ILOSTAT. Accessed June 18, 2024. https://ilostat.ilo.org/data/.
